data.description: Discover your dream home! This spacious 3 bedroom house boasts a modern and open design, perfect for lving and entertaining. Step onto the wood look ceramic tile that add a touch of elegance. Plush carpet in bedrooms offer cozy comfort. Primary bedroom is split for added privacy with a stylish bathroom with frameless shower, double sinks, and ample closet space. Enjoy the luxury of an oversized lot, offering ample space for outdoor activites or gardening and covered patio area. Unwind in the kitchen as you prepare meals with the convenience of stainless appliances and lots of granite counters. This home is more than just a house; it's a lifestyle with community amenities, and it is waiting for you to make it your own. Do not miss the opportunity to see this one soon. Create your forever home here on this inviting cul-de-sac. Seller needs possession until the end of November currently as they are building a new home. ***
